text: Polypedates iskandari is a species of frogs in the family Rhacophoridae. It is endemic to Sulawesi, Indonesia. ==References== * Riyanto, Mumpuni & McGuire, 2011 : Morphometry of striped tree frogs, Polypedates leucomystax (Gravenhorst, 1829) from Indonesia with description of a new species. title: Polypedates iskandari
